ion of scattered TNOs, contributing significantly to the longevity of\nthese objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Jul 2007 16:32:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2007 08:12:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-11"}
