ls are 33 and 16 M_sun pc^-3 for the NFW\nand the Einasto profiles, respectively. For the cored Burkert profile, this\nvalue is 0.06 M_sun pc^-3.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2007 11:10:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Sep 2008 10:12:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-09-02"}
